One time  Nollywood actress turned entrepreneur, Carolyna Hutchings failed to control her emotion when she opened up about her child’s heart condition. The beautiful mother of three opened up about her daughter’s heart condition during the third episode of the rising reality TV show, Real Housewives of Lagos. Carolyna, who had hosted other cast of the show at a Bohemian-themed party brokedown in tears when she was misjudged by another cast of the show, Laura Ikeji.   Nnaji Charity says religion has destroyed many homes     Nigerian Idol 7: Adekunle Gold, Kingdom thrill audience as…     Tillaman, Princess Adedoja mourn dad, Alaafin of Oyo   “My daughter has two holes in her heart. I have been preventing this from the public. She had a heart condition since her birth. I have always prayed for a girl and the only girl I have was born with a medical condition. She has two holes in her heart. Do you know what I go through, do you know what I am going through to take care of her?” she thundered while reacting to Ikeji’s claims. Ikeji had told Iyabo Ojo that the reason she loathed Carolyna was that she was badmouthing her big sister and blogger, Linda Ikeji. She also said this was why she refused to attend the beach get-together organised by Ojo for all the cast of the show. Carolyna broke down in tears in the presence of Toyin Lawani, Iyabo Ojo, Chioma Ikokwu, and Laura Ikeji. The alluring Carolyna went further to say she would have loved to save her marriage and would have wanted to enjoy her marriage to Nigerian billionaire Musa Danjuma but for some misconceptions, top of which was a story written by Linda Ikeji that she had her daughter for another man.